# This directory stores user data generated by the gym-ai-trainer agent:
# - user.md: User profile and preferences
# - goals.md: Training goals and progress
# - workouts.json: Cached workout data from Hevy
# - routines.json: Cached routines from Hevy (API only)
# - conversation.md: Conversation history with compaction
#
# These files are gitignored (except this .gitkeep) to protect user privacy.
